All scripts tested only in OS/2-environment.

clean.cmd	Clean up: remove all *.obj, *.lib, *.err etc...
make.cmd	Make OS/2 or windows binaries
		(into bin\%platform%\firecast.exe)
store.cmd	Make package of sources (into firecast-sources-NNNNNNNN.zip)
		!! need PKZIP.EXE

bin\firecast.cmd	Make firecast's package (OS/2) for distribution
			!! need PKZIP.EXE
                        (into bin\OS2\firecast-NNNNNNNN.zip)

bin\firecast.iss	Script for Inno Setup
                        (make installer for windows into bin\NT\Output\setup.exe)
	I use Inno Setup 5.1.6 under eComStation (OS/2) via Odin.

